   </p>
  </td>
  <td>
   <p>
    <label for="style_quoted_archive_text">
     Style Quoted Message Text
    </label>
    <br />
    Lines that start with a &quot;&gt;&quot; will be styled like this:</p>
    <blockquote>
     <p>
      <span class="quoted_reply">
       &gt; This is quoted text!
      </span>
     </p>
    </blockquote>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

